data.description: Welcome to 1245 William Street...your new dream home located on one of the most desired streets in the heart of Federal Hill! This beautiful 2 bed, 2 full bath gem boasts a perfect blend of modern amenities and rustic charm. As you step inside, you'll immediately notice the inviting exposed brick walls that add character and warmth to the living spaces. The rustic wood floors enhance the cozy atmosphere and provide a timeless appeal. The built-in shelves are perfect for displaying your favorite books, collectibles, or artwork. The kitchen is a chef's dream, with stainless steel appliances, espresso cabinets, and beautiful granite countertops. The bar seating and additional table space provide plenty of room for both casual meals and entertaining guests. Whether you're preparing a gourmet feast or enjoying a morning cup of coffee, this kitchen is designed for style and functionality. Upstairs, you'll find that the primary suite is a true retreat, featuring a generously sized en-suite bath, ample closet space, and a skylight in the vaulted ceiling that bathes the room in natural light. The hallway leads to your convenient laundry closet, making chores a breeze, as well as a 2nd full bath with a linen closet for your storage needs. But that's not all! This property also has the exciting potential to build a rooftop deck with ready-to-go access from the second bedroom/office space. Imagine enjoying breathtaking views of the city skyline and hosting gatherings under the open sky. You want more? How about a large parking pad to ensure you always have a dedicated space for your ride, an unfinished basement with ample storage space, making it easy to keep your home organized and clutter-free, and newer HVAC condenser (replaced in 2021) for year-round comfort. This home's convenient location provides easy access to local amenities, restaurants, and entertainment, adding to its overall appeal. Don't miss the opportunity to make this exquisite property your new home. Schedule a showing today and experience the perfect blend of contemporary living and classic charm that 1245 William Street has to offer. ***SELLER NOW OFFERING $5,000 TOWARDS A 2/1 RATE BUY DOWN OR CLOSING COSTS FOR A FULL PRICE OFFER.***
